OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782411505
OL,3,CTwo boa constrictor snakes found on
OL,4,CDarlington golf course
OL,6,FProfessional golfer Aaron Cox tells
OL,7,FKris Jepson of his surprise at having
OL,8,Fto remove two boa constrictor snakes
OL,9,Ffrom a Darlington golf course
OL,11,FA professional golfer has had to
OL,12,Fremove two boa constrictor snakes from
OL,13,Fthe long grass at a Darlington golf
OL,14,Fcourse on two separate occasions
OL,15,Fwithin a week.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
