OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782411505
OL,3,CTwo boa constrictor snakes found on
OL,4,CDarlington golf course
OL,6,FAaron Cox, who has had to deal with
OL,7,Fsnakes before in his native Australia,
OL,8,Fsaid he was shocked to find the snakes
OL,9,Fon two different days, just off the
OL,10,Ffairway of the course at Blackwell
OL,11,FGrange Golf course, where he teaches
OL,12,Fgolf.
OL,14,FHe told ITV News Tyne Tees: "One of my
OL,15,Fjuniors actually hit her tee shot and
OL,16,Fit finished on the snake.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782411505
OL,3,CTwo boa constrictor snakes found on
OL,4,CDarlington golf course
OL,6,F"She wasn't very happy with hitting
OL,7,Fthe ball from it, so I got the wedge
OL,8,Fand got the ball away from it, but the
OL,9,Fkids were like, 'we're taking photos
OL,10,Fof this', so they were quite happy
OL,11,Fwith that.
OL,13,F"I had to flatten a lot of that long
OL,14,Fgrass. I put the box down next to it,
OL,15,Frolled it on it's side and the just
OL,16,Ftried to push it in.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
