OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782411505
OL,3,CTwo boa constrictor snakes found on
OL,4,CDarlington golf course
OL,6,F"Then obviously all the jokes started,
OL,7,Fyou know, the Mick Dundee lines and
OL,8,Fthe Steve Irwin lines, and all that,
OL,9,Fso it was a bit of fun, but at the
OL,10,Fsame time it was a serious thing."
OL,12,FThe first snake was located on
OL,13,FSaturday 13 June and the second a week
OL,14,Flater. It is believed the snakes
OL,15,Fsuffered from a fatal disease, and
OL,16,Fsince Aaron rescued them from the
OL,17,Fcourse and took them to a reptile
OL,18,Fshop, they have both died.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
