PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782411505
OL,3,CTwo boa constrictor snakes found on
OL,4,CDarlington golf course
OL,6,FWhen he first attempted to move the
OL,7,Fsnakes, Aaron said he was cautious,
OL,8,Fadding: "I was quite shocked, because
OL,9,FI never thought I'd really find a
OL,10,Fsnake in the North East of England, so
OL,11,FI wasn't sure exactly whether I should
OL,12,Fpick it up, whether I should touch it,
OL,13,Fif it was poisonous, so I was a bit
OL,14,Freluctant.
OL,16,F"I kind of had to pick it up or move
OL,17,Fit to try and get it in the box to get
OL,18,Fit out and off the course, and to the
OL,19,Freptile shop."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
