OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782411505
OL,3,CTwo boa constrictor snakes found on
OL,4,CDarlington golf course
OL,6,FThe first snake was believed to be
OL,7,Faround 6 feet long, but Aaron said the
OL,8,Fsecond snake was even bigger and
OL,9,Fheavier.
OL,11,FHe said: "It felt bigger. It looked
OL,12,Fbigger, so I got that one into a box
OL,13,Fas well, but I actually had to pick
OL,14,Fthat one up. He had a go at me, which
OL,15,FI had to move back pretty quickly.
OL,17,F"You could hear it hissing. You could
OL,18,Fhear it was trying to rattle off
OL,19,Faround the box, so he wasn't happy."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782411505
OL,3,CTwo boa constrictor snakes found on
OL,4,CDarlington golf course
OL,6,FAaron Cox said the RSPCA were
OL,7,Finterested in talking to anyone with
OL,8,Finformation about how the snakes ended
OL,9,Fup abandoned near the golf course and
OL,10,Fsaid he felt it was a cruel act.
OL,12,FHe said: "It was obviously a snake
OL,13,Ffrom South America, which means it's a
OL,14,Fpet snake. The poor thing was just
OL,15,Fdumped. If the owners of it didn't
OL,16,Fwant it, well they should have taken
OL,17,Fit to the RSPCA, they should have
OL,18,Ftaken it to a pet shop. I just think
OL,19,Fthat was an unfortunately bad way to
OL,20,Fdo it, and cruel really."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
